The state of the whole system evolves into-
\begin{equation}
	\vert \psi\rangle   =\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}(\vert R\rangle   \vert D_{1}\rangle   +\vert L\rangle   \vert D_{2}\rangle)   \label{eq:first-entangled-state}
